    "Title": "RESOURCE DRIVE: MEDIUM SHIPMENT",
    "Description": "Your work for us has not gone unnoticed, we really appreciate it.\n\nIf you have a ship that can accommodate a shipment of <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize) cargo containers</EM4> and a heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4>, we need you to head to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and collect the cargo there. You should be fine to complete this by yourself, but if you\u2019re in a hurry, you might want to consider <EM4>bringing a friend</EM4> with you.\n\nWhen you\u2019ve finished collecting the cargo from the freight elevator, place it on a freight elevator at: <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address|ListAll)</EM4>. We have staff on hand that will process the delivery from there.\n\nThank you for your help as always.\n\n\nDenver Samuels\nContractor Liaison Officer\nCrusader Industries",
